parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the roof panel can cause it to detach from the vehicle, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Wind noise entering the vehicle
creaking or popping sounds from the roof
roof panel separation or detachment
white residue on dashboard and door panels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the door to open spontaneously, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Driver-side door opens independently
door lock actuator failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the stability control system can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: "Check stability control system" warning message
loss of vehicle control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defects in the dashboard and door panels can cause aesthetic issues and potentially lead to further problems.
symptoms: White residue on dashboard and door panels.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the active handling system can cause the vehicle to brake or steer unexpectedly, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The "Service Active Handling" warning message appears on the dashboard
the vehicle brakes independently
the vehicle pulls to one side
the steering wheel jerks or locks
and the vehicle shakes or vibrates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause loss of power steering assist, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering fluid leaks
the power steering pump fails
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
and the vehicle vibrates or shakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to lock or jerk, leading to loss of control, accidents, or near-misses.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks or jerks
the "Service Active Handling" warning message appears on the dashboard
and the vehicle pulls to one side.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded, especially at night or in low-visibility conditions.
symptoms: The headlights suddenly turn off
the low beam headlights fail to illuminate
the headlights only work intermittently
the headlights do not turn on at all.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electronic stability control can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The electronic stability control warning light comes on without any tire spin or condition that would warrant it
the warning light comes on when turning from a standstill
the warning light comes on when driving on sand or slippery surfaces.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Leak/Fuel Odor from Driver's Side Fuel Tank
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fuel leak/fuel odor from the driver's side fuel tank can cause a fire hazard, especially when the vehicle is parked in a garage or near an open flame. This can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Strong smell of fuel
fuel leaks from driver's side fuel tank
fuel tracks down the side of the tank
puddle of fuel under the driver's side tank
fuel smell in the cabin
fuel smell in the garage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Low beam headlights shut off without warning
intermittent headlight failure
high beams work but low beams do not.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety-critical systems to malfunction, including the headlights, brakes, and engine.
symptoms: Active handling system warning light appears
brakes feel different
engine idles differently
faulty connection in the wiring harness.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the shifter can cause the vehicle to become stuck in park, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Automatic shifter gets stuck in park
shifter lock solenoid fails
unable to shift out of park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the battery to drain, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Check charging system light comes on
voltage gauge reads 11.5V
alternator failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the valve can cause engine damage, leading to costly repairs and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Valve rattle
engine noise
potential engine failure.
